0643913", "stars": 2531, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 340953, "username": "Warren1027", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Warren1027", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f7d/8770/340953_mini.png?m=1679290172", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f7d/8770/340953_normal.png?m=1679290172", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f7d/8770/340953_large.png?m=1679290172", "created": 1534206694, "last_modified": 1679290172}, "last_reply_by": "Warren1027", "last_touched": 1679366523, "title": "分享 3HK 的 esim 使用体验", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/925540", "created": 1679292580, "deleted": 0, "content": "上周开了一张香港的 esim ，是 3HK 的 DIY 储值卡  \r\n套餐是 268 港币一年，40G 通用流量+5G 社交定向流量，大陆香港澳门均可使用  \r\n大陆地区漫游使用的话，不用实名  \r\n![]( https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/b977fd1c82695d89.jpeg)  \r\n![]( https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/ad0ac36de04038a5.jpeg)  \r\n![]( https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/af723a3c0566db46.jpg)  \r\n![]( https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/b8338423eff2da4c.jpg)  \r\n在大陆漫游，是中国联通的运营商，可以直接开启 LTE 网络，直接扶墙  \r\n总体来说，体验还是不错的，这个号码还能拿来接受验证码等。  \r\n储值卡不能开启 WiFi Calling ，不够漫游状态下接打电话还是蛮贵的。", "content_rendered": "<p>上周开了一张香港的 esim ，是 3HK 的 DIY 储值卡<br/>\n套餐是 268 港币一年，40G 通用流量+5G 社交定向流量，大陆香港澳门均可使用<br/>\n大陆地区漫游使用的话，不用实名<br/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/b977fd1c82695d89.jpeg\"/><br/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/ad0ac36de04038a5.jpeg\"/><br/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/af723a3c0566db46.jpg\"/><br/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/03/20/b8338423eff2da4c.jpg\"/><br/>\n在大陆漫游，是中国联通的运营商，可以直接开启 LTE 网络，直接扶墙<br/>\n总体来说，体验还是不错的，这个号码还能拿来接受验证码等。<br/>\n储值卡不能开启 WiFi Calling ，不够漫游状态下接打电话还是蛮贵的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1679292580, "replies": 56, "id": 925540}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 1536, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 1490, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 601724, "username": "believingsee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/believingsee", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/937aa37d208c475755f1c3c5f56466bd?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/937aa37d208c475755f1c3c5f56466bd?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/937aa37d208c475755f1c3c5f56466bd?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1668403812, "last_modified": 1668403812}, "last_reply_by": "WindProtect", "last_touched": 1679367666, "title": "最近父亲要换辆燃油车，本人目前座驾是新能源，好久没留意过油车了，大家推荐几款让我直接抄个作业", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/925736", "created": 1679361214, "deleted": 0, "content": "预算 20w 左右\r\n\r\n-不要混动\r\n-只要合资（老爷子开一辈子国产了，满足他合资的一个小愿望）\r\n-丰本 尽量不要\r\n-有 L2\r\n-小毛病少一点，机械素质相对稳定的\r\n-中保研安全性优秀", "content_rendered": "预算 20w 左右<br /><br />-不要混动<br />-只要合资（老爷子开一辈子国产了，满足他合资的一个小愿望）<br />-丰本 尽量不要<br />-有 L2<br />-小毛病少一点，机械素质相对稳定的<br />-中保研安全性优秀", "last_modified": 1679361399, "replies": 47, "id": 925736}]